	source/mircoders/servlet/ServletModuleLinksImcs.java,
	source/mircoders/servlet/ServletModuleMessage.java: i18n-feature
	based on kellans proposal implemented. the resource-bundles are
	located in the directory mir/bundles and build.xml copies them to
	WEB-INF/classes/. to get a localized message just type
	${message(key)} into a admintemplate. in the properties-file the
	hash look like key=value. the properties-files are named in the
	following way: admin_??.properties ( ?? stands for the languagecode
	) . the admin.properties without languagecode is the
	standard-bundle

